OL,3,CNorth East academic pays tribute to
OL,4,C'one-off' Dr Michael Mosley
OL,6,FA friend and colleague of the late Dr
OL,7,FMichael Mosley has joined, describing
OL,8,Fhim as 'a real-one off'.
OL,10,FThe body of the 67-year-old was found
OL,11,Fin a rocky area near Agia Marina beach
OL,12,Fon the Greek island of Symi days after
OL,13,Fhe went missing.
OL,15,FDr Mosley was known for his
OL,16,Fappearances in shows such as the BBC
OL,17,Fseries Trust Me, I'm A Doctor and for
OL,18,Fhis involvement in the Fast 800 Diet -
OL,19,Fwhich was inspired by the work of
OL,20,FProfessor Roy Taylor, an academic at
OL,21,FNewcastle University.
