OL,4,C'one-off' Dr Michael Mosley
OL,6,FProfessor Roy Taylor met Dr Mosley
OL,7,Fthrough his research into type 2
OL,8,Fdiabetes. It was to be the beginning
OL,9,Fof a long friendship and fruitful
OL,10,Fworking relationship.
OL,12,FHe said: "Michael was fascinated by
OL,13,Fthis because he had developed type 2
OL,14,Fdiabetes, he had lost weight himself
OL,15,Fand found it had gone away, so hearing
OL,16,Fthat there was an explanation, he came
OL,17,Fup here hot-foot.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
