OL,3,CNorth East academic pays tribute to
OL,4,C'one-off' Dr Michael Mosley
OL,6,F"Michael is just a real one-off, a
OL,7,Ftremendous person. We hit it off
OL,8,Fstraight away. He was endlessly
OL,9,Fcharming, enthusiastic, enquiring and
OL,10,Fentertaining.
OL,12,F"He is going to be sadly missed,
OL,13,Fbecause there are few other people in
OL,14,Fthis space of giving authoritative
OL,15,Fadvice in a way that's accessible and
OL,16,Funderstandable to everyone."
OL,18,FDr Mosley's work is now part of a
OL,19,Fnational programme which supports
OL,20,Fpeople with the illness.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
