OL,3,CNorth East academic pays tribute to
OL,4,C'one-off' Dr Michael Mosley
OL,6,F"It's been a tremendous honour to know
OL,7,Fthe man, to laugh with him and to have
OL,8,Fa good time with him and also to work
OL,9,Fwith him in spreading the information,
OL,10,Flearning about taking this research
OL,11,Fforward and making it fully effective
OL,12,Ffor not just for people in Britain but
OL,13,Fthis has spread throughout the world",
OL,14,Frecalled Professor Taylor.
OL,16,FProfessor Roy Taylor reminisced on
OL,17,Fmemories with dear friend and
OL,18,Fcolleague, Dr Michael Mosely
