OL,3,CNorth East academic pays tribute to
OL,4,C'one-off' Dr Michael Mosley
OL,6,FThe Newcastle University academic
OL,7,Frecounted one particular time where Dr
OL,8,FMosley's personality shone through on
OL,9,Fa visit to Gateshead.
OL,11,FHe said: "I've been lucky enough to
OL,12,Fappear on stage with him a couple of
OL,13,Ftimes. One of those times, at the Sage
OL,14,Fin Gateshead, he had actually broken
OL,15,Fhis ankle. He had a big protective
OL,16,Fboot and was hobbling and I wondered
OL,17,Fhow he was going to make his
OL,18,Fappearance.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
