OL,3,CNorth East academic pays tribute to
OL,4,C'one-off' Dr Michael Mosley
OL,6,F"Michael true to form zoomed onto the
OL,7,Fstage, roared up to the microphone and
OL,8,Fsaid 'hello everybody!' He was on a
OL,9,Fsimple scooter. His bad leg, he was
OL,10,Fkneeling on the scooter.
OL,12,F"Here's the man who could overcome
OL,13,Fdisabilities, see the positive and get
OL,14,Fthe most out of a situation. I think
OL,15,Fthat for me encapsulates his spirit,
OL,16,Fand that's what will live on in his
OL,17,Fmemory."
